<!-- ═══════════ WHAT IT IS ═══════════ -->
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">What It Is</div>
    <h2>A healing arts workshop, brought to your community</h2>
    <p class="lede">A 60–80 minute facilitated experience where participants fold an origami crane, write a personal peace message, and send both into a worldwide exchange network. No arts experience needed. Every voice belongs.</p>

    <div class="what-grid">
      <div class="what-card">
        <h3>Real Connection</h3>
        <p>Your crane and your words travel to someone across the world.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="what-card">
        <h3>Global Belonging</h3>
        <p>Part of a peace network active in 150+ countries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="what-card">
        <h3>Fully Accessible</h3>
        <p>All ability levels welcome. Arthritis-friendly adaptations available.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════ HOW IT WORKS ═══════════ -->
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">How A Session Works</div>
    <h2>Four simple phases</h2>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Open</h4>
          <p>Story and grounding to set the tone for the session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Fold</h4>
          <p>Guided crane-making and writing, step by step, at your group's pace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Reflect</h4>
          <p>Circle sharing — open to all, pressure-free.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">4</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Send</h4>
          <p>Cranes travel into the exchange — and in time, one comes back.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="partner-strip">
      <div class="partner-text">
        DPCI is offered <strong>in partnership with the Peace Crane Project</strong>, a global peace initiative connecting communities through folded cranes and written messages.
      </div>
      <a class="partner-link" href="https://peacecraneproject.org/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Learn about the Peace Crane Project →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

